  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Scaling up Solar Energy use for Rural Electrification in Sierra Leone</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is designed to build on the pilot solar energy project implemented in Kono district. The project falls within the context of the West Africa climate change programme framework focusing provision of lighting for domestic uses and fostering lighting -based income generating activities for households and small businesses. This will be achieved through identification and installation of appropriate and affordable solar home systems, capacity building of partners and community committees on installation and maintenance of solar equipments, advocacy and research.</narrative>
  </description>
